A '''lime''' is a [[fan fiction]] story that stops short of full, explicit descriptions of sexual activity. A common analogy is that a lime is characterized by PG-13 level explicitness, as opposed to the NC-17 level explicitness characterizing a [[lemon (anime)|lemon]].  Alternatively, the difference is that a lime includes everything up to, but not including, penetration.  The nomenclature derives from a lemon and lime being similar but distinct fruits.

Other forms of limes are those stories that approach an intimate scene, and then go "off-camera", with the intimacy left to the reader's imagination. As with the other terms of this type, the orientation of the characters involved (such as the slash [[yaoi]] and [[Yuri (animation)|yuri]] pairings) are not as important as the kind of intimate activity engaged in.

